description: Rachel's Cafe & Creperie is taking their gourmet goodness on the go in Lancaster! These are fresh crepes, made specially for you when you order--pair them with the wonderful coffee, espresso, or tea, and you'll feel just like you're in a cozy cafe. Rachel's is bringing you delicious food, wonderful service, and an experience you'll always remember, so don't miss out when this truck rolls your way!
name: Rachel's Cafe & Creperie
